text:
Very disappointed in the owners attitude, I understand why mom and pop pet shops are falling off the map. Have some consideration and support local breeders and propagate the hobby. 50 Fathoms will be getting my business from  here on out. It's a shame this place is closer and used to be my go too.....
In Responce;
It wasn't the fact that you don't deal with local hobbyists. It was your attitude. I run a small business as well and for my nephew to look at me when we got in the truck and ask me if you and I had a bad business deal or something means you made a sever negative impact on him as well. I was very disappointed as for years you were my go to guy.
